data.description: This home will blow your mind on the space it has to offer so go ahead and step into your beautifully updated Ranch home! You'll notice all new flooring throughout along with freshly painted walls. Just off the main living area you'll find split bedrooms for a touch of privacy. In the Primary Bedroom you won't be lacking closet space because there are 2 Walk IN Closet's perfect for a fashionista! The main bathroom is nothing short of pinterest perfect! You'll then step into your kitchen that has stainless steel appliances, updated countertops and cabinets along with a shiplap wall to get it that farmhouse touch. Step down into your dining area with a see through pantry, again did I mention Pinterest perfect? From the dining area you can walk out onto your newly renovated covered deck that overlooks a generous size fenced in back yard perfect for entertaining and cookouts. This home has an additional 884 Sq Ft of living space! As you walk down the hallway you'll come into another family room along with 3 large bedrooms. This home will not disappoint and is also located in a No outlet road which means less through traffic. Hurry Fast cause this one won't last!
